✅ 1️⃣ Lucide React install
npm install lucide-react
2️⃣ Import and use icons in your React component
import { Home, User } from "lucide-react";
export default function App() {
  return (
    <div className="flex gap-4">
      <Home size={24} color="blue" />
      <User size={24} color="green" />
    </div>
  );
}
3️⃣ Optional: Using with Tailwind CSS

If you use Tailwind, you can style icons like any other element:

<Home className="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" />
